Package: ginkos-sysinfo
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Rizalina Mingazheva <your@email.com>
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10), python3-rich, dpkg
Recommends: ginkos-defaults
Description: GinkOS system information and manifest validation tools
 Provides three utilities:
   gink-info   — displays system info and manifest status on login
   gink-freeze — snapshots installed packages into a pinned manifest
   gink-audit  — full drift report comparing system to manifest
 These tools implement GinkOS's core design principle: every
 deployment is auditable and reproducible.
